data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled in the heart of Tuscaloosa. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the hardwood floors gracefully flowing throughout the living spaces. The spacious living room is perfect for relaxing with family and friends, featuring ample natural light. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and elegant granite countertops. Additionally, this home offers a large backyard, ready for your creative touch. New wiring has been installed throughout the house, ensuring safety and efficiency, along with a new vapor barrier that safeguards the home's integrity. Home was fully remodeled in 2017. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, parks, and schools. Don't miss your chance to own this beautiful home!
